<div
  id="{% if section.settings.nav_id != empty %}custom-nav-{{ section.settings.nav_id }}{% endif %}"
  class="x-one-brand-endorsement-{{ section.id }}"
>
  <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement">
    <img
      class="pc lazyload x-one-brand-endorsement-img"
      data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/Why_Choose_Procolored.jpg?v=1770976983"
      alt=""
    >
    <img
      class="mb lazyload x-one-brand-endorsement-img"
      data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/Why_Choose_Procolored__mb.jpg?v=1770977025"
      alt=""
    >
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-title">Why Choose Procolored!</div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc">
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc-text">
          <span>With deep-rooted expertise since 2018</span>
          , Procolored drives the future of customization with industry-leading DTF, UV, and UV-DTF solutions. We have
          spent years mastering UV printing technology to empower creators to transform fabric, acrylic, wood, metal,
          and ceramics into vibrant, professional-grade prints.
        </div>
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc-text">
          Certified with the <span>G7 Master Facility Qualification</span>, the
          <span>Gold Standard for global color precision</span>, we guarantee that what you see on screen is exactly
          what you get in production, ensuring unrivaled quality in every project.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-img pc">
        <img
          class="lazyload "
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/Global_No.jpg?v=1771049778"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-img mb">
        <img
          class="lazyload"
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/Frame_2121235845.jpg?v=1771049789"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-desc">
        Recognized as a leading brand in the desktop inkjet printing industry, our growth is powered by the trust of
        <span>200,000+</span> users worldwide. Customers choose Procolored for printers that are built to last and easy
        to use. By bringing industrial-grade precision into a desktop format, we empower creators to produce
        high-quality custom products — without the complexity of industrial systems.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-img pc">
        <img
          class="lazyload "
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/180W.jpg?v=1770976996"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-img mb">
        <img
          class="lazyload"
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/180W__mb.jpg?v=1770977025"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-desc">
        Procolored's previous generation — the K Series DTF printer — was a standout success on Kickstarter,
        <span>raising nearly $1.8M </span>and <span>attracting hundreds of backers.</span> This milestone not only
        validated Procolored’s product design and user experience but also helped build global momentum for our next
        generation of production-grade systems.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
